data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the sought after gated community of Los Reyes Canyon. You are greeted into this home with an abundance of windows allowing natural light to pour into every angle. The formal sitting room is located just off the entryway and allows for seamless connection to the kitchen and dining room. A peaceful office has been well-thought out and allows for a quiet place to work from home or study. The kitchen is a chef's dream complete with stainless steel appliances, ample storage space in the upper and lower cabinets, and a sizable island. The family room offers oversized windows, a wood burning fireplace and a picturesque view of the backyard. Retreat to your luxurious primary bedroom with outdoor access to the wooden deck. There is no shortage of space for your wardrobe or accessories with a spacious walk-in closet complete with built-in shelving. Three sizable bedrooms and a loft area at the top of the stairs, finish off the interior of this home.The backyard is a sprawling oasis that offers a perfect blend of relaxation and charm. At its heart is a spacious covered patio, providing a shaded retreat for outdoor gatherings and leisurely moments. The deck extends seamlessly from the house, creating a natural transition between indoor and outdoor living spaces. Shed is available for additional storage; measures 12x16. Don't miss out on the opportunity to turn this dream home into your reality, with its prime location just minutes away from some of San Antonio's most renowned attractions and its abundance of space, you won't want to miss out! Schedule a showing today!
